{"title":"永不放下枪","authors":["徐先国"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不放下枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少尉　徐先国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢郭老称赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们去向地球开战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起科学技术大旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲过艰难战胜自然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心交给党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄解甲重上战场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是当年整装上舰艇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是当年横戈渡长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿女离队要北上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响应号令远征北大荒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用拿枪的手把起锄头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强迫土地交出食粮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让血迹浸染的军装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受到机油和泥土的奖赏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让子弹穿透的疤伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黑土地上泛红发光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心交给党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄解甲永不放下枪"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}